2. DATASETS
The datasets included in this package are derived from various sources 
and are subject to the following license terms:

-----------------------------------------------------------------------
DATASET: rota
- Infection data: The use of data from the SurvStat@RKI 2.0 application is permitted,
  with proper attribution to the Robert Koch Institute (RKI):
  "Source: Robert Koch Institute (RKI), SurvStat@RKI 2.0, https://survstat.rki.de, accessed on 2025-02-03."
- Population/Census data: Federal Statistical Office of Germany (Destatis). 
  Licensed under Data Licence Germany – Attribution – Version 2.0 
  (DL-DE -> BY-2.0).
  Source: https://www.govdata.de/dl-de/by-2-0

DATASET: chickenpox
- Source: UCI Machine Learning Repository / Hungarian Central Statistical Office.
  Licensed under Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International (CC BY 4.0).

DATASET: SST
- Source: Derived from the 'STRbook' R package (Wikle et al., 2019).
  Used with attribution to the original authors and their work.
-----------------------------------------------------------------------

3. ATTRIBUTION & MODIFICATIONS
In accordance with the licenses above:
- Any modifications to the original data (preprocessing, filtering, 
  aggregation) have been performed by the package author.
- For detailed source URLs and retrieval dates, please refer to the 
  R documentation for each dataset (e.g., help(rota), help(chickenpox), help(SST)).